poster: F R I 3 N D Z
title: Heya guys, I just wanted to share my stream with you!
body:
Hello there,
I'm a fairly nice dude from Germany whos streaming his journeys through the gold and platinum ranks.
I've been playing league since season 1 pretty much and have seen a lot of funny and good stuff since
then, but also the bad sides of this game. 
I would say even though Im not highly ranked, im pretty experienced when it comes to league.

I dont expect you to hang in my stream all day, would just be nice if you could come and hang out with me a bit x)

I'm currently on a tryhard-run where I really tryhard to win my games, to get back to platinum, since I had a really
rough start in season 5 so far, with a lot of personal stuff but also a bad mindset coming into the games, which
really has changed :)


Cya guys then! x)

twitch.tv/huepie
